                            <comment id="13784191" author="ndimiduk" created="Wed, 2 Oct 2013 17:34:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Is there a MAVEN ticket for this?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13784195" author="eclark" created="Wed, 2 Oct 2013 17:39:34 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://jira.codehaus.org/browse/MNG-1378&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://jira.codehaus.org/browse/MNG-1378&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13784196" author="nkeywal" created="Wed, 2 Oct 2013 17:39:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;In anycase, it&apos;s a nice improvement imho: people should not have to depends on the tests jar to get the mini clusters helpers.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13784383" author="eclark" created="Wed, 2 Oct 2013 20:19:50 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Here&apos;s the patch that adds hbase-testing-util.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Here&apos;s an example of using it:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/elliottneilclark/hbase-downstreamer&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://github.com/elliottneilclark/hbase-downstreamer&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13784392" author="jmhsieh" created="Wed, 2 Oct 2013 20:29:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;interesting - this doesn&apos;t pull the mini-cluster out but pulls all the dependencies in.  Do you think it makes sense to pull out the minicluster as a separate module (I believe that is what the hadoop-minicluster modules does over there)&lt;/p&gt;
</comment>
                            <comment id="13784396" author="eclark" created="Wed, 2 Oct 2013 20:31:23 +0000"  >&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;I believe that is what the hadoop-minicluster modules does over ther&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Nope I followed what they do exactly. &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/hadoop-common/tree/trunk/hadoop-minicluster&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/hadoop-common/tree/trunk/hadoop-minicluster&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;I did this because otherwise it gets really tricky.  Tests in the hbase-server module would then depend on a module that depends on hbase-server.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13784416" author="jmhsieh" created="Wed, 2 Oct 2013 20:54:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;nice.  +1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13784507" author="eclark" created="Wed, 2 Oct 2013 22:00:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Committed.  I&apos;ll add a release note in a second.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
